creator: BlixtBit Pty. Ltd.
descriptionHtml:
Report and Run: Integrate is a collaborative Cloud-based image reporting tool. This app helps anyone create reports by capturing images, writing notes, and adding annotations. Reports, in the field, are automatically synced to the cloud so they can be shared with team members and stakeholders and can be accessed and edited from anywhere.

Features:

* Capture images or add them from the gallery
* Add text boxes to images and add annotations such as lines, circles, crosses, ticks, and polygons using gesture recognition
* Save time and improve quality by using commonly used phrases
* Reports are stored in the cloud as they are created and accessible from anywhere.
* Organize your reports as you want with a directory structure, e.g., by project, division, client
* Distributed workflow - the reports can be created in the field and then polished in the office.
* Collect important information - properties can be assigned to images and reports such as the responsible person, start date, end date, status, and quality.


Report and Run: Integrate is the latest release of the Report and Run brand. We have supported a wide range of industries such as construction, engineering, architecture, real-estate, insurance, education, inspections, and commercial cleaning to name a few. This system can be used with a wide range of reporting styles from a general purpose image report to a defect/snag type report, your imagination is the limit..

For more information or just enquiries please contact us at support@reportandrun.com.
